OL,5, Boris Johnson has been criticised by   
OL,6, his standards adviser over an official 
OL,7, inquiry into the refurbishment of his  
OL,8, Downing Street flat.                   
OL,10,FMr Johnson apologised to Lord Geidt    
OL,11,Fthat he had not seen messages the PM   
OL,12,Fexchanged with a Tory peer who         
OL,13,Finitially paid for the revamp.         
OL,15,FThe messages were revealed during a    
OL,16,Fseparate inquiry by the elections      
OL,17,Fwatchdog on how the works were funded. 
OL,19,FLord Geidt said it demonstrated        
OL,20,F"insufficient" respect for his role.   
